{"tid":170512,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"交通意外對方唔肯賠錢","createTime":"2017-03-24T17:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T17:46:36.000Z","uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3ff2199efcdb33a6dca341522e75275dcf948c","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"架車之前俾人hi 花左，<br />\n見對方都有say 哂sorry,話整完照賠番，咁就簽左和解紙，寫番車房整完實報實銷咁賠，但宜家佢話嫌貴唔肯俾，可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n係唔係唯一方法報警去小額錢債追？<br />\n但聽講小額錢債好廢，嬴左都未必拎得番錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有經驗幫下手"},{"pid":"07ba9ffce5f5de60c749722fca8b78ec0be2ea85","tid":170512,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:58:53.000Z","msg":"未收錢簽乜嘢和解紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4af73717b220add45a2924495b5482c64901582","tid":170512,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未收錢簽乜嘢和解紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家啲人真係on9 未和解完成又走去簽<br />\n和解左又唔撚簽 搞到比人反咬多啖"},{"pid":"34d7d9ea4292e0552d7b0f6ca25eddbe96d76fb0","tid":170512,"uid":17611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:21:14.000Z","msg":"不嬲收晒錢先簽和解紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13528516ae8c68cbf59983a491b796b7d3992787","tid":170512,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:03:54.000Z","msg":"講到明和解紙梗係和咗解先簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a12cb2fc814faa2a061731d7260145dc1cf8edd","tid":170512,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁佢唔肯賠就報交通部啦"},{"pid":"f529fd80fb6fd0119030530aecededde6162ac53","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未收錢簽乜嘢和解紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家啲人真係on9 未和解完成又走去簽<br />\n和解左又唔撚簽 搞到比人反咬多啖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果下撞完又未知要整幾錢，以為簽左張紙寫明會包整番果part 就ok(都係噴番油幾千蚊）<br />\n我on9 左咁宜家係唔係無野做到？？"},{"pid":"2e145bc3b18338b4b13ac6f6a1f3b3da7585f1f6","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢唔肯賠就報交通部啦</blockquote><br />\n 過左報警有用？<br />\n過程係我泊係路邊，佢double park hi 花左我"},{"pid":"dd9773942147f1c55661408c1a7a84eea8cb9136","tid":170512,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:01:02.000Z","msg":"整花人架車D陷家剷死全家"},{"pid":"f67ef5b15f8f9ce3974334e428e4155d55fcc1b0","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整花人架車D陷家剷死全家</blockquote><br />\n咁又禍不及妻兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b75a34f7df59017d06c6eb708387a27c103c8f8","tid":170512,"uid":4959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T23:57:33.000Z","msg":"車台真係咩on9仔都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64760623e0731b12677619721a7b7d29792ae74","tid":170512,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢唔肯賠就報交通部啦</blockquote><br />\n口同鼻拗，有cam都無用，實俾黑警曬鳩你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw未解決 簽乜和解紙"},{"pid":"c636810a5fd04af26a33bdb3b9642e1d1534bb6e","tid":170512,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd05c6a72b5fa99c3090b95f874e7144ae368c6","tid":170512,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:07:56.000Z","msg":"和解紙係民事合約，要睇你張紙點寫，如果寫得好清晰係有應付未付，要待實際報價後再畀錢，呢個係有條件合約，對方未履行，而對方現對唔肯履行，算係毀約。<br />\n<br />\n當然，應付未付部分，對方質疑報價唔合理，呢個係可爭論之處。<br />\n<br />\n想搞大件事可以照報警，和解紙只係民事和解，並不影響黑警執行刑事檢控權力，當然黑警會否進行刑事檢控就另一件事。"},{"pid":"0804b8a887e171afae8accf33692f4f43f42507e","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>和解紙係民事合約，要睇你張紙點寫，如果寫得好清晰係有應付未付，要待實際報價後再畀錢，呢個係有條件合約，對方未履行，而對方現對唔肯履行，算係毀約。<br />\n<br />\n當然，應付未付部分，對方質疑報價唔合理，呢個係可爭論之處。<br />\n<br />\n想搞大件事可以照報警，和解紙只係民事和解，並不影響黑警執行刑事檢控權力，當然黑警會否進行刑事檢控就另一件事。</blockquote><br />\n當初就係知黑警黎都係叫我地自己解決，所以先無報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de91f23b5ce9d32e377e298c301ee7866eff3857","tid":170512,"uid":45132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"669b4899a0bf03d6ce6b40a68bfeeb586f97e0e4","tid":170512,"uid":1589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢點解要賠？<br />\n呢個係憑佢自己本事和解返黎既賠償金<br />\n係佢叻仔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062820eee4bcaa2bb77bcbf200d75ab242dbabf0","tid":170512,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢點解要賠？<br />\n呢個係憑佢自己本事和解返黎既賠償金<br />\n係佢叻仔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896eb22a929b86e23cc5a3dbb5c2fc1e196ce2fc","tid":170512,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"正常做法：<br />\n交通意外後一定要報警做記錄<br />\n，如果十日內唔和解要搵交通部<br />\n如果無報過警就好Q 麻煩，因為無證據，佢唔認數你吹佢唔漲（除非有cctv/其你車cam 影到）<br />\n你而家唯一做法：撞車地點搵返所屬既交通部到報案<br />\n例如你係大圍撞既就搵返新界南交通部問下（ 帶齊資料 咩車牌，對方司機資料，有無現場影相？）睇下個邊點同你搞"},{"pid":"a0f50b46abd51847cdbe8c4cbc51c28471f388f4","tid":170512,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"你和解左 已經冇得追數"},{"pid":"e7a38f7c0b49fa5c2b88d878e086875678f9b17e","tid":170512,"uid":18105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常做法：<br />\n交通意外後一定要報警做記錄<br />\n，如果十日內唔和解要搵交通部<br />\n如果無報過警就好Q 麻煩，因為無證據，佢唔認數你吹佢唔漲（除非有cctv/其你車cam 影到）<br />\n你而家唯一做法：撞車地點搵返所屬既交通部到報案<br />\n例如你係大圍撞既就搵返新界南交通部問下（ 帶齊資料 咩車牌，對方司機資料，有無現場影相？）睇下個邊點同你搞</blockquote><br />\nsor,睇唔到簽左和解紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   樓主自己俾整車喇"},{"pid":"3ceedad7c561a4c21d9e51464f6433f4af699d8b","tid":170512,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁on9,幾千蚊當買個教訓"},{"pid":"9ff55485b79a56c15993a3d0e03e05dece4434fe","tid":170512,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"on9真係無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4414cd26e7756a12e1e7d370059d69b62e1c092","tid":170512,"uid":16580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"和解紙寫<br />\n對方願意賠償右邊車門噴油一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次當on9,咁下次應該點？<br />\n個問題係即時報唔到價，咁照報警，交俾保險搞？"},{"pid":"87afc3947fd7305db174f885bd24e24f89f0b9bf","t